Ritual Claws of the Scion 
<br />
MAGIC ITEM LORE ITEM NO DROP
<br />
Slot: PRIMARY
<br />
STR: +5 STA: +8 WIS: +10 INT: +10 HP: +80 MANA: +80
<br />
SV COLD: +20
<br />
Recommended level of 65.
<br />
