Seems to me that an ordinary stat aug is hardly worth the trouble of constantly switching off a summoned orb for the ornate orb. Not to mention the fact that other gear is in a constant state of upgrade and stat needs differ accordingly. The only stat boosting aug that would make sense to me would be the <span style="font-weight: bold">"Sparkling Quartz of Resistance"  +5 MR +5 CR +5 FR.</span> At least this gives you some diversity but all in all I think I will go with a melee aug. I think we can all agree that stat boosters can go just about anywhere but the same cannot be said for melee augs.
<br />

