<br />

<br />
Am I going to go in everytime and be a mage tank? Heck no (though being a <span style="font-style: italic">human</span> mage slightly improves the chances of doing that successfully).. but there are times when something like that could be useful. Hmmmm. Can you life-tap greenies? There's a thought  <img src="images/smiles/icon_idea.gif" alt="Idea" border="0" /> 
