				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I switch my primary between staff of the silent star and Orb of Mastery.
<br />

<br />
I honestly LOVE the Orb of Mastery, I think it's the best looking weapon in the game and I'm proud to have it.  Having said that, there are times when I need the +HP or other resists offered by my other staff.
<br />

<br />
If I was going to buy a proc augment, I would put it into my staff of the silent star which already has a good proc.  If I was to augment the Orb, I would augment it in such a way that made it more desirable to equip for stats.  Probably HP, or resists.<br />_________________<br /><Center><b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=36994" target="_blank" class="postlink">Sage Eandori Raintree</a></b>
<br />
<a href="http://www.eqempyreal.com" target="_blank" class="postlink">Empyreal</a> - Solusek Ro Server
